  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><strong>Saint\n        Mary Woolnoth</strong><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>St. Mary Woolnoth is a church in the \"Unreal\n        City\" of London (the financial district); the crowd\n        is flowing across the London Bridge to work in the City.\n        (NA)</p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>link two</td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Saint Mary Woolnoth St. Mary Woolnoth is a church in the \"Unreal City\" of London (the financial district); the crowd is flowing across the London Bridge to work in the City. (NA) reference topics link two back to \"The Waste Land\"",
